Ed Setrakian https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ed_Setrakian 0 Ed Setrakian (born October 1, 1928 in Anawalt, West Virginia, USA) is an American actor of film and television. Setrakian is known for appearing in the films Tough Guys Don't Dance and Zodiac and the television programs The Sopranos (in the episode Where's Johnny?) and Person of Interest (in two episodes as Grifoni). Setrakian has also played four different roles in the Law Order franchise. Ed_Setrakian ( born October_1_,_1928 in Anawalt , West_Virginia , USA ) is an_American_actor of film_and_television .
